    "description": "<p>You can spend <strong>2 AP</strong> to call on your deity to intervene on your&nbsp;behalf when your need is great to replenish you and your&nbsp;allies.</p>\n<p>Make a <strong>DC 10 Spell Check</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Success: </strong>You gain a pool of <strong>Divine Points </strong>equal to your level&nbsp;that you can use to replenish any number of creatures within&nbsp;5 Spaces of you, distributing the <strong>Divine Points </strong>among them.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>A creature regains 2 HP for each <strong>Divine Point </strong>they receive. Additionally you regain an amount of <strong>MP</strong> equal to your <strong>Prime Modifier</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Success (each 5): </strong>You gain additional Divine Points equal to&nbsp;your Prime Modifier.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>System Tip:&nbsp;</strong>You can select \"Channel Divinity\" as \"Other Item\" on <strong>Usage</strong> Tab. That way you will use charge of &nbsp;\"Channel Divinity\" &nbsp;automatically when using that item.</em></p>",
